# 🌐 Rayeh - Product Rental Platform

**Rayeh** is a simple and attractive website for renting products like photography gear, event tools, dresses, and more. It’s designed to be user-friendly with no login required.

---

## 🖼️ Screenshots

![Website screenshot](assest/img/screenshot-home.png)

---

## 💡 Features

- ✅ Responsive design for all devices
- ✅ Browse products by category
- ✅ Easy rental request form without login
- ✅ Elegant interface with a signature turquoise color (#00BFA6)
- ✅ Optional fake login page

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

🔗 [View it live on GitHub Pages](https://latifaalnaaimi.github.io/rayeh/)

---

## 🛠️ Built With

